<p>Help Center</p><p><br></p><p>Welcome to the UserVault Help Center. Find answers to common questions below.</p><p><br></p><p>Getting Started</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I create an account?</p><p>A: Click "Sign Up" and enter your email, username, and password. Verify your email to activate your account.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: I forgot my password. What do I do?</p><p>A: Click "Forgot Password" on the login page and follow the instructions sent to your email.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I change my profile information?</p><p>A: Go to Settings → Profile and update your information.</p><p><br></p><p>Live Streaming</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I start a live stream?</p><p>A: Click "Go Live" in the navigation menu. Configure your streaming software (OBS) with the provided stream key and server URL.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: What are the stream requirements?</p><p>A: We recommend 1080p resolution, 30fps, and a bitrate of 3000-6000 kbps.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Why isn't my stream showing up?</p><p>A: Check your internet connection, verify your stream key is correct</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Can I save past streams?</p><p>A: Stream recording features are coming soon.</p><p><br></p><p>Payments and Purchases</p><p><br></p><p>Q: What payment methods do you accept?</p><p>A: comming soon</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I cancel a subscription?</p><p>A: comming soon</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Can I get a refund?</p><p>A: Refund requests are reviewed on a case-by-case basis. Contact support@uservault.net for assistance.</p><p><br></p><p>Account and Security</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I enable two-factor authentication?</p><p>A: Go to Settings → Security and enable 2FA (coming soon).</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I delete my account?</p><p>A: Go to Settings → Account → Delete Account. This action is permanent and cannot be undone.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: My account was hacked. What should I do?</p><p>A: Immediately change your password and contact support@uservault.net.</p><p><br></p><p>Content and Community</p><p><br></p><p>Q: What content is allowed on UserVault?</p><p>A: Content must comply with our Terms of Service. Illegal, harmful, or abusive content is prohibited.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: How do I report inappropriate content?</p><p>A: Click the "Report" button on any post or stream.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Can I block users?</p><p>A: Yes, go to a user's profile and click "Block" (feature coming soon).</p><p><br></p><p>Technical Issues</p><p><br></p><p>Q: The website isn't loading. What should I do?</p><p>A: Clear your browser cache, disable browser extensions, or try a different browser.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: Videos aren't playing.</p><p>A: Ensure your browser is up-to-date and JavaScript is enabled.</p><p><br></p><p>Q: I'm experiencing lag during streams.</p><p>A: Check your internet speed, reduce stream quality, or contact your ISP.</p><p><br></p><p>Still Need Help?</p><p><br></p><p>Contact our support team at: support@uservault.net</p><p><br></p><p>We're here to help!</p><p><br></p>